Rev	Revelation
Ro	Romans
Ru	Ruth
SS	Song of Solomon
Tit	Titus
Zec	Zechariah
Zep	Zephaniah
 

 

 

Other abbreviations and special symbols used:

 

S	Shorter ending of Mark
T	Psalm titles
†	A Dagger distinguishes “LORD” and “GOD” from “Lord” and “God” in Hebrew Bible references
→	An arrow following an entry heading points to related words for additional study
 	Contexts in double brackets are from passages that are similarly bracketed in the NRSV (e.g., John 7:53—8:11)
For further study consult The Concise Concordance to the New Revised Standard Version (Oxford University Press, 1993) and The NRSV Concordance Unabridged (Zondervan, 1991).


—John R. Kohlenberger III

 

